rams on ABC, NBC, and CBS in the Los Angeles, Memphis region.<\\/p><p>Latreal Mitchell is the proud Founder and CEO of Fitness Bunch, a foundation helping to educate children and parents about childhood obesity. She has run afterschool programs, school assemblies, and classroom visits to discuss the importance of healthy eating and exercise to children. She partnered with The American Heart Association and conducted workouts for the kids before teaching them how to plant and grow their vegetables through AHA\\u2019s Teaching Garden Program.<\\/p><p>Latreal holds multiple certifications in Personal Training, Group Fitness, Corrective Exercise, Functional Range Conditioning, Yoga, and Youth Exercise. She also has her nutrition certifications with Precision Nutrition and the Institute for Integrative Nutrition. In the fitness industry for over 20 years, her training and certifications have enhanced her knowledge of the importance of functional movement, exercise, supplementation, and nutrition for adults and children.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#505050\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"typography_line_height\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.5,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.3,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"f9ed5cf\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"La\'s website: <span style=\\\"color:#E1B03A\\\"> www.latrealmitchell.com <\\/span>\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"www.latrealmitchell.com\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"},\"title_color\":\"#505050\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":24,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_size_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":12,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\",\"typo