e\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Felicia Fdyfil-Horne\\n\",\"title_color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":32,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\",\"typography_line_height\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.5,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.5,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"7886207\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Executive Director \\/Psychotherapist, LCSW\\n\",\"title_color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":24,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"80d2001\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Felicia Fdyfil-Horne LCSW is a social work entrepreneur, therapist, educator, advocate, and leader in the field. Felicia is dedicated to creating a safe space for healing.<\\/p><p>Felicia has more than 15 years of experience working with mental health agencies that partner with the child welfare system and the children System of Care; including roles providing crisis intervention therapy, trauma focused therapy, individual and family therapy, and Clinical Supervision. (and helping individuals and families find hope in working toward achieving their goals through the collaborative effort of utilizing therapeutic interventions while working within a multi-disciplinary team.)<\\/p><p>Ms. Fdyfil-Horne has been trained in various evidence-based practices of trauma treatment, including EMDR ( Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing), ( ARC (Attachment Self-Regulation and Competence) and Felicia is certified in TF-CBT (Trauma Focused Cognitive Behavioral Therapy). Her passion for trauma- informed care extends to supporting culturally inclusive policies and practices. Felicia believes that it could be said that all of therapy is built on a foundation of hope. The hope that one\'s habits, behaviors, emotions, outlooks, problems, and relationships can change leading to progress and committing to doing the work. I believe that with the proper techniques and the desire to work toward a better tomorrow, progress can be achieved.<\\/p><p>Felicia is passionate about ending the mental health stigma that prevents black and brown communities from taking the step of seeing a therapist. This passion led Felicia to starting a mental health agency developed to present mental health topics in a way that feels more accessible and relevant.<\\/p><p>Felicia is the founder and owner of Hope Therapeutic Services, a group private practice and mental health agency located in West Orange, NJ. Hope Therapeutic Services provides therapeutic services to over 1,000 clients annually. HOPE was founded based on the passion and commitment in helping individuals and families find hope through the power of building your own internal and external resources.\\u2019<\\/p><p>Felicia is also the founder of Hope Lives Here a 501\\u00a93. Hope Lives Here is a youth development component of Hope Therapeutic Services, a community-based mental health service provider that has successfully served more than 800 youth since 2016.<\\/p><p>Felicia holds a Masters of Social Work from Columbia University and she is a Licensed Clinical Social Worker (LCSW). Felicia received her Master of Social Work (MSW) degree from Columbia University School of Social Work. Additionally, Felicia is Chair of the Essex County NJ-NASW chapter and she sits on the Board of Trustees for both Family Connections, Inc. and Partners for Health Foundation.<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_size_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":12,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"typography_line_height\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.5,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.3,\"sizes\":[]},\"_padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"c894f46\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Felicia\'s website:  <span style=\\\"color:#E1B03A\\\"> www.hopetsllc.com<\\/span>\\n\\n\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"www.latrealmitchell.com\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"},\"title_color\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":24,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_size_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":12,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\",\"typography_line_height\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.5,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.5,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"2357e2d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
