0\",\"left\":\"20\",\"isLinked\":false},\"padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"1699863\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"d6eaaf1\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Jamie L. Tajan \",\"title_color\":\"#505050\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":32,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\",\"typography_line_height\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.5,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.5,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"6457d54\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Owner \\/ Luxury Travel Advisor, IATAN Certified Agent \",\"title_color\":\"#505050\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":24,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"fc790e9\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>Jamie\\u2019s love for travel began in 1998 on her first international flight EVER to the beautiful Caribbean islands.\\u00a0 That was the spark that ignited her passion for travel.\\u00a0 She has been fortunate enough to be able to travel for leisure and business to several 5star, ultra-luxury destinations.\\u00a0 In 2007 she decided to become an independent affiliate of Travel by Divine Inc and launch A World to Sea Travel.\\u00a0 This has allowed her to not only share her expertise with clients, it has allowed her to focus on her passion, continue to expand her knowledge and turn a hobby into a successful business.\\u00a0 \\u00a0<\\/p><p>Jamie is a natural planner at heart. She has always been the \\u201cgo-to\\u201d to plan events, gatherings, trips, etc.\\u00a0 Her love for travel and talent for planning go hand in hand.\\u00a0 Travel planning, whether it\\u2019s for herself or for her clients, is more than just booking a beautiful resort in a different country.\\u00a0 It\\u2019s designing an experience that gives her clients moments to reflect, enjoy, be present, and truly experience the culture. A stress free, memorable experience from beginning to end.\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Her current areas of expertise in the travel industry:\\u00a0<\\/p><p>Group Travel, Luxury Concierge Travel, Luxury Villas, Caribbean, Mexico, Italy, England, Maui, Beijing, Thailand, Singapore, Canada, USA<\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#505050\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":16,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_size_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":12,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\",\"typography_line_height\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.5,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.3,\"sizes\":[]},\"_padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"cd1fb8a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Jamie\'s website:  <span style=\\\"color:#E1B03A\\\"> \\nwww.latrealmitchell.com<\\/span>\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"www.latrealmitchell.com\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"},\"title_color\":\"#505050\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Montserrat\",\"typography_font_size\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":24,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_size_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":12,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_font_weight\":\"600\",\"typography_line_height\":{\"unit\":\"em\",\"size\":1.5,\"sizes\":[]},\"typography_letter_spacing\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":0.5,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"7729f68\",\"