(69, 1, '2021-05-08 11:07:19', '2021-05-08 11:07:19', '<h2>MAKE YOUR MIND, BODY,</br> & SOUL beautiful</h2>		\n		<h4>Our mission is to inspire individuals and couples to live life to their fullest potential by aligning their Mental, External, and Internal body as one.</h4>		\n										<img width=\"454\" height=\"454\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-1.jpg 454w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-1-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\" />											\n										<img width=\"454\" height=\"454\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-2.jpg 454w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-2-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-2-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-2-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\" />											\n										<img width=\"454\" height=\"454\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-3.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-3.jpg 454w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-3-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-3-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/what-we-beliave-3-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 454px) 100vw, 454px\" />											\n			<h2>What we  believe \n</h2>		\n		<p>At MEI Wellness, we firmly believe that you cannot reach your wellness goals without balancing your mind, body, and spirit. The importance of Mental health gets continuously overlooked and is often stigmatized. We believe that mental health is a vital component of ones overall health. Our goal is to create a safe space to empower, build skills, and strengthen relationships. Mental also encompasses your spirituality, and we believe in the power of meditation and other mindfulness activities and grounding techniques.</p><p>The mental health benefits of meditation include better focus and concentration, improved self-awareness and self-love, and reducing stress and anxiety levels. Exercise is something we have confidence in and is the E in external. Exercise has many proven benefits, including weight loss, strengthens your bones and muscles, improves your sleep, and the list goes on. But we believe without a strong M; the E can be forgotten. Finally, we believe that the Internal, which is how you fuel your body, is pivotal in bringing it all together. Good nutrition helps with mood, depression, prevents diseases, keeps your heart healthy, and is your fountain of youth. We believe that you should trust in MEI to help you reach your wellness goals and create a better relationship with yourself and others.</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '47-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-08 11:07:19', '2021-05-08 11:07:19', '', 47, 'http://localhost/meiwell/2021/05/08/47-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
