(178, 1, '2021-05-10 09:19:12', '2021-05-10 09:19:12', '<h2>meet team emi</h2>		\n										<img width=\"431\" height=\"431\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-one.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-one.jpg 431w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-one-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-one-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-one-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n			<h2>Latreal M. Mitchell\n</h2>		\n			<h2>Celebrity Fitness Trainer\n</h2>		\n		<p>Latreal Mitchell is one of the top Celebrity Trainers and Health &amp; Wellness Experts in the industry. She has been featured in magazines like Good Housekeeping, Womens Day, Shape, SELF, Mens Fitness, Muscle &amp; Fitness, and EDGE magazine, all highlighting exercise routines and her work with adults, athletes, and children. She was also the Columnist for Good Housekeeping Magazine for over two years, creating exercise routines and fitness content for their readers. As a Figure Competitor for more than five years, she demonstrated physical transformation. She used this knowledge to benefit her clients. In addition to fitness magazines, she has appeared on television programs like Revenge Body with Khloe Kardashian on E! for three seasons. With multiple appearances on shows like Good Morning America, LIVE with Kelly and Michael, The Steve Harvey Show, The Doctors, The View, Here and Now, and local news programs on ABC, NBC, and CBS in the Los Angeles, Memphis region.</p><p>Latreal Mitchell is the proud Founder and CEO of Fitness Bunch, a foundation helping to educate children and parents about childhood obesity. She has run afterschool programs, school assemblies, and classroom visits to discuss the importance of healthy eating and exercise to children. She partnered with The American Heart Association and conducted workouts for the kids before teaching them how to plant and grow their vegetables through AHAs Teaching Garden Program.</p><p>Latreal holds multiple certifications in Personal Training, Group Fitness, Corrective Exercise, Functional Range Conditioning, Yoga, and Youth Exercise. She also has her nutrition certifications with Precision Nutrition and the Institute for Integrative Nutrition. In the fitness industry for over 20 years, her training and certifications have enhanced her knowledge of the importance of functional movement, exercise, supplementation, and nutrition for adults and children.</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://www.latrealmitchell.com\">La\'s website:  www.latrealmitchell.com </a></h2>		\n										<img width=\"431\" height=\"431\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-two.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-two.jpg 431w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-two-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-two-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-member-two-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Desktop-middle-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n			<h2>Felicia Fdyfil-Horne\n</h2>		\n			<h2>Executive Director /Psychotherapist, LCSW\n</h2>		\n		<p>Felicia Fdyfil-Horne LCSW is a social work entrepreneur, therapist, educator, advocate, and leader in the field. Felicia is dedicated to creating a safe space for healing.</p><p>Felicia has more than 15 years of experience working with mental health agencies that partner with the child welfare system and the children System of Care; including roles providing crisis intervention therapy, trauma focused therapy, individual and family therapy, and Clinical Supervision. (and helping individuals and families find hope in working toward achieving their goals through the collaborative effort of utilizing therapeutic interventions while working within a multi-disciplinary team.)</p><p>Ms. Fdyfil-Horne has been trained in various evidence-based practices of trauma treatment, including EMDR ( Eye Movement Desensitization and Reprocessing), ( ARC (Attachment Self-Regulation and Competence) and Felicia is certified in TF-CBT (Trauma Focused Cognitive Behavioral Therapy). Her passion for trauma- informed care extends to supporting culturally inclusive policies and practices. Felicia believes that it could be said that all of therapy is built on a foundation of hope. The hope that one\'s habits, behaviors, emotions, outlooks, problems, and relationships can change leading to progress and committing to doing the work. I believe that with the proper techniques and the desire to work toward a better tomorrow, progress can be achieved.</p><p>Felicia is passionate about ending the mental health stigma that prevents black and brown communities from taking the step of seeing a therapist. This passion led Felicia to starting a mental health agency developed to present mental health topics in a way that feels more accessible and relevant.</p><p>Felicia is the founder and owner of Hope Therapeutic Services, a group private practice and mental health agency located in West Orange, NJ. Hope Therapeutic Services provides therapeutic services to over 1,000 clients annually. HOPE was founded based on the passion and commitment in helping individuals and families find hope through the power of building your own internal and external resources.</p><p>Felicia is also the founder of Hope Lives Here a 5013. Hope Lives Here is a youth development component of Hope Therapeutic Services, a community-based mental health service provider that has successfully served more than 800 youth since 2016.</p><p>Felicia holds a Masters of Social Work from Columbia University and she is a Licensed Clinical Social Worker (LCSW). Felicia received her Master of Social Work (MSW) degree from Columbia University School of Social Work. Additionally, Felicia is Chair of the Essex County NJ-NASW chapter and she sits on the Board of Trustees for both Family Connections, Inc. and Partners for Health Foundation.</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://www.latrealmitchell.com\">Felicia\'s website:   www.hopetsllc.com\n</a></h2>		\n										<img width=\"431\" height=\"431\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Member-three.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Member-three.jpg 431w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Member-three-300x300.jpg 300w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Member-three-150x150.jpg 150w, http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-Member-three-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 431px) 100vw, 431px\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n			<h2>Jamie L. Tajan </h2>		\n			<h2>Owner / Luxury Travel Advisor, IATAN Certified Agent </h2>		\n		<p>Jamies love for travel began in 1998 on her first international flight EVER to the beautiful Caribbean islands. That was the spark that ignited her passion for travel. She has been fortunate enough to be able to travel for leisure and business to several 5star, ultra-luxury destinations. In 2007 she decided to become an independent affiliate of Travel by Divine Inc and launch A World to Sea Travel. This has allowed her to not only share her expertise with clients, it has allowed her to focus on her passion, continue to expand her knowledge and turn a hobby into a successful business. </p><p>Jamie is a natural planner at heart. She has always been the go-to to plan events, gatherings, trips, etc. Her love for travel and talent for planning go hand in hand. Travel planning, whether its for herself or for her clients, is more than just booking a beautiful resort in a different country. Its designing an experience that gives her clients moments to reflect, enjoy, be present, and truly experience the culture. A stress free, memorable experience from beginning to end.</p><p>Her current areas of expertise in the travel industry:</p><p>Group Travel, Luxury Concierge Travel, Luxury Villas, Caribbean, Mexico, Italy, England, Maui, Beijing, Thailand, Singapore, Canada, USA</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://www.latrealmitchell.com\">Jamie\'s website:   \nwww.latrealmitchell.com</a></h2>', 'Emi Team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'emi-team', '', '', '2021-05-10 10:38:27', '2021-05-10 10:38:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost/meiwell/?page_id=178', 0, 'page', '', 0),
