/>											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"65\" height=\"65\" src=\"http://localhost/meiwell/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/Mei-Team-page-small-bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n			<h2>Latreal M. Mitchell\n</h2>		\n			<h2>Celebrity Fitness Trainer\n</h2>		\n		<p>Latreal Mitchell is one of the top Celebrity Trainers and Health &amp; Wellness Experts in the industry. She has been featured in magazines like Good Housekeeping, Womens Day, Shape, SELF, Mens Fitness, Muscle &amp; Fitness, and EDGE magazine, all highlighting exercise routines and her work with adults, athletes, and children. She was also the Columnist for Good Housekeeping Magazine for over two years, creating exercise routines and fitness content for their readers. As a Figure Competitor for more than five years, she demonstrated physical transformation. She used this knowledge to benefit her clients. In addition to fitness magazines, she has appeared on television programs like Revenge Body with Khloe Kardashian on E! for three seasons. With multiple appearances on shows like Good Morning America, LIVE with Kelly and Michael, The Steve Harvey Show, The Doctors, The View, Here and Now, and local news programs on ABC, NBC, and CBS in the Los Angeles, Memphis region.</p><p>Latreal Mitchell is the proud Founder and CEO of Fitness Bunch, a foundation helping to educate children and parents about childhood obesity. She has run afterschool programs, school assemblies, and classroom visits to discuss the importance of healthy eating and exercise to children. She partnered with The American Heart Association and conducted workouts for the kids before teaching them how to plant and grow their vegetables through AHAs Teaching Garden Program.</p><p>Latreal holds multiple certifications in Personal Training, Group Fitness, Corrective Exercise, Functional Range Conditioning, Yoga, and Youth Exercise. She also has her nutrition certifications with Precision Nutrition and the Institute for Integrative Nutrition. In the fitness industry for over 20 years, her training and certifications have enhanced her knowledge of the importance of functional movement, exercise, supplementation, and nutrition for adults and children.</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://www.latrealmitchell.com\">La\'s website:  www.latrealmitchell.com </a></h2>', 'Emi Team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '178-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-05-10 10:15:06', '2021-05-10 10:15:06', '', 178, 'http://localhost/meiwell/2021/05/10/178-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
